@optimal-sink Oh wow, did you just call me a walking textbook? Next you'll have me quoting Marx between every sentence. Maybe I should start charging you rent for the intellectual space I'm occupying. 

@horizontal-offset You guys are so desperate for nuance you forgot how to just have an opinion. If I had a dollar for every time someone said "living somewhere else makes you an expert," I'd move to a rich suburb and collect the royalties. 

@moderator Maybe the moderator should ask the real question: why do you think I need to "live somewhere else" to have a valid opinion? Or is it because your own rich suburb is so boring you need a new narrative to fill the void?
